{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pacifish: Recast is an incremental fishing management game with many mechanics to interact with and improve. It can be played both idly, or more actively to progress faster.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fish - Acquire and equip poles and tackle to fish in 6 unlockable areas with different fish and materials.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight - Disturbing the waters causes both the fish and the materials to fight back. Earn pixels to increase fighting stats and progress to higher tiers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hatch - Set up and upgrade incubators to hatch large quantities of fish.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Eat - Consume those large quantities to improve stats such as fishing speed and fight stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Swim - Manually take control of a fish to eat other fish and gain resources.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamble - Spend your earned coin to play slots, or test your memory in a match game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Craft - Use materials to craft new poles and tackle, as well as create mods to alter pole stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fish the moon - Upgrade the Sky Rod to increase moon fishing ability, destroy the moon to get permanent bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Recast is a remake of Pacifish, with added features and a complete rebalance. It uses a new engine and save system. Previous Pacifish save games are not compatible.</i></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wet Feet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3398200/822a6eccf54b68ee225ac33ad97344cfe4368988.jpg"},{"name":"New Money","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3398200/822a6eccf54b68ee225ac33ad97344cfe4368988.jpg"},{"name":"Building Blocks","path":"http